教學方法 Teaching Strategies
      Students are responsible to attend the classes, participate in discussion, and study the distributed handouts and assigned textbooks.
■Students should be familiar with the knowledge of the geriatric PT assessment tools, especially the most recent evidence.
■Students need to choose one of the assessment tools, apply it to his/ her final project and present the results and discuss its relationship with literature. 
     

