參考書目
 
1. *Umphred
DA. Neurological rehabilitation, 4th ed. St. Louis: Mosby, 2001. 
2. *O'Sullivan
SB, Schmitz TJ (eds). 2001. Physical Rehabilitation Assessment and Treatment.
4th ed. FA Davis:Philadelphia. (Assigned reading) 
3. *Somers
FM. Spinal cord injury-functional rehabilitation, 2nd ed. New Jersy:
Prentice Hall, 2001. (Assigned reading)
4. *Shumway-Cook
A, Woollacott MH. Motor Control : Theory and Practical Applications. Lippincott
Williams & Wilkins, 2001.
5. Carr
J and Shepherd RB. Neurologic Rehabilitation: Optimizing Motor Performance.
1999. (Strongly recommended)
6. Bromley
I. 1991. Tetraplegia and paraplegia: a guide for physiotherapists. 4th ed.
Churchill Livingstone: London.
7. Sawner
KA, Lavigne JM. Brunnstrom’s movement therapy in hemiplegia: a
neurophysiological approach, 2nd ed. Philadelphia: Lippincott, 1992.
8. Bobath
B. Adult hemiplegia: evaluation and treatment, 3rd ed. Oxford:
Butterworth/Heinemann, 1990.
9. Johnstone
M. Therapy for stroke: building on experience. Edinburgh: Churchill
Livingstone, 1991.
 
評分方法
期末考90%;
上課表現及平時成績
10%







